Customized onboarding content can help users understand and interpret the data, make informed decisions, and act based on the latest information. To set up customized onboarding, follow these steps:

Select the widget where you want to add the Learn option.
Enter a title for the frame that presents your resource.
Enter the URL for your video or webpage.
Click Preview your content to see what your users experience.
(Optional) Add custom onboarding for multiple charts.

Provide the URL to a site that doesn’t prevent embedding.
If your resource is secured, instruct users to authenticate so that the resource can appear in the onboarding frame.
For best results with YouTube, provide your video’s embed URL.
Keep in mind that while the onboarding frame allows linking to other webpages, browser controls such as Back and Refresh aren’t accessible.
title: Customize Onboarding with CRM Analytics
